node.title: Brian Laundrie died of a self-inflicted gunshot wound, attorney says
node.description: Laundrie died from a self-inflicted gunshot wound to the head, his family's attorney said Tuesday.
node.content: ["Brian Laundrie died from a self-inflicted gunshot wound to the head and his manner of death was suicide, his family's attorney Steven Bertolino said Tuesday. His human remains were found last month at a Florida reserve after a weeks-long manhunt following the disappearance and death of his fiancee, Gabby Petito.\u00a0", "\"Chris and Roberta Laundrie have been informed the cause of death was a gunshot wound to the head and the manner of death was suicide,\" Bertolino said in a statement. \"Chris and Roberta are still mourning the loss of their son and are hopeful that these findings bring closure to both families.\"", "This story is developing.\u00a0", "Tori B. Powell is a breaking news reporter at CBS News. Reach her at tori.powell@viacomcbs.com"]
